{"tid":1405983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日各位要照顧埋地鐵以外既地方","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:17:32.000Z","uid":270398,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"355f8411ac7188761cc6742ae6fb949e03184f05","tid":1405983,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"除左塞地鐵之外唔該塞埋條路, 頭先落街食野聽到一群港豬話聽日地鐵班友一定又會黎搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 聽日早少少出門口搭巴士/小巴啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 早少少班友邊會咁神心咁早黎到阻到我地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以聽日大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 今日早睡早起, 要早過早班車行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 地鐵同主要道路就一定要搵人招呼架啦, 不過有D人番工路線可能比較短, 大家諗下有冇方法塞埋呢D人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 塞巴士總站有冇得諗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2bb7c14b231a69abd66a252a4cdd80df846b75","tid":1405983,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"a56707aa0fa3d413cb0c5d035487ad53a88861d2","tid":1405983,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"863103301f9d8c7f201d4ee643376bf35eefe9b9","tid":1405983,"uid":231110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"集中資源啦，唔通D人唔駛搭車/落樓下番工都同佢諗埋咩"},{"pid":"cacb8130a54b7933c307718051df001a1d43b275","tid":1405983,"uid":267235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:10:06.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 借位推post<br />\n<br />\n【8.5三罷】如果朝早所有人遊車河!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404800</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cc3YftZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2F